Motion Detection Alarm System
This is a Python-based motion detection system that triggers an alarm sound and sends notifications via email and SMS when motion is detected through a webcam.

Features
    Motion detection using OpenCV.
    Alarm sound when motion is detected.
    Email and SMS alerts.
Requirements
    Python 3.x
    Libraries: opencv-python, imutils
    Webcam
    Installation


Install the required libraries:

    pip install opencv-python imutils

    Set up your email credentials in the script.
    Usage


Run the script:

        python motion_alarm_system.py
        
        Press t to toggle alarm mode, and q to quit.
